{
  "stem": "11184.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--there, you know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but they were grabbing the people to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there-- see, people were digging-- what do you call?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Trenches, yeah, that, that--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To hide.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the people were grabbed to cover them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 165,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took-- they took the people right away to hard work--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and hitting them and mistreating them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 166,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some were killed right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 167,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not that I--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 168,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--only, you know-- people were talking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 169,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and, and then--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was-- a nice lady just took him in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 170,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was-- a family-- a family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 171,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he stayed with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish people, Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they felt sorry for him to be all alone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- you know, he said how many people were killed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 172,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The bombs were flying from all--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 173,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the sides.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 173,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't remember that much--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 174,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--all the details what he--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--was saying.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then every day you had another announcement by the Germans, new laws, new laws.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jews are supposed not to go here, not to go there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then the Jews have to wear the armband, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 175,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then-- and then they were throwing people out of their homes--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 176,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the rich ones, taking everything away from them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 177,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's the same building.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 178,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, not ours.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 178,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not ours.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 178,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went to the more expensive neighborhoods--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and would take everything away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then came another announcement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 179,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we all have to leave to leave the, the houses and move into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, posted.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 180,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, and leaflets would come in--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 181,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--you know yeah, mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember the armband.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 182,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 183,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I think we bought them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 184,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think you, you bought them, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 185,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
